  "recipeIngredient": [
    "1 1/2 quarts Beef broth",
    "46 ounces V-8 Juice",
    "2 cups Water",
    "1 cup Diced celery",
    "1 cup Diced peeled potatoes",
    "1 cup Chopped onions",
    "1 cup Sliced carrots",
    "3/4 cup Uncooked barley",
    "4 cloves Garlic, minced",
    "2 tablespoons Italian seasoning",
    "1 teaspoon Lemon-pepper seasoning",
    "1 teaspoon Dried rosemary, crushed",
    "1 teaspoon Fennel seed",
    "1 teaspoon Dried mint",
    "Parmesan cheese, optional"
  ],
  "recipeInstructions": "1. In a large kettle or Dutch oven, combine all ingredients except the cheese.\n2. Bring to a boil.\n3. Reduce heat and cover.\n4. Simmer for 3 hours.\n5. Serve each portion topped with cheese if desired.\n6. Yields 12-14 servings (3 1/4 quarts).",
